    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-11-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-11-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="666"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d666">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Swenson</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-11-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 27, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Article III, amended convention, is worded identically as heretofore. Your
                    despatch names three millions, the convention three millions and a quarter.
                    Cable corrections.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Swenson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
